---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Terms & Conditions — Fatima Saleh" description="Terms and conditions for services provided by Fatima Saleh.">
  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-16 sm:py-24">
    <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-semibold mb-2">Terms &amp; Conditions</h1>
    <p class="text-muted text-sm mb-10">Last updated: March 2025</p>

    <div class="prose prose-neutral max-w-none space-y-8 text-ink/90 leading-relaxed">

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">1. About these terms</h2>
        <p>
          These terms and conditions govern the use of this website and the provision of services by
          <strong>Fatima Saleh</strong>, a sole trader operating in the United Kingdom.
          By engaging my services or using this website, you agree to these terms.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-3">
          These terms should be read alongside any specific agreement or proposal provided to you before
          work commences. In the event of a conflict, the specific agreement takes precedence.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">2. Services</h2>
        <p>
          I provide coaching, facilitation, organisational development consultancy, and related advisory
          services. The scope, deliverables, timeline, and fees for any engagement will be agreed in writing
          before work begins.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-3">
          I reserve the right to decline or discontinue a client engagement if I determine it is not a
          suitable fit, subject to any obligations set out in a signed agreement.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">3. Fees and payment</h2>
        <p>
          Fees are agreed on a per-project or retainer basis and confirmed in writing prior to commencement.
          Invoices are issued on the schedule set out in the relevant agreement.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-3">
          Payment terms are <strong>30 days from invoice date</strong> unless otherwise agreed in writing.
          Late payments may incur interest in accordance with the Late Payment of Commercial Debts Act 1998.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-3">
          A deposit may be required for new engagements. The amount and refund conditions will be
          stated in the project agreement.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">4. Intellectual property</h2>
        <p>
          Unless otherwise agreed in writing, all materials, frameworks, and tools I develop during an
          engagement remain my intellectual property. I grant clients a non-exclusive licence to use
          deliverables for their own internal purposes.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-3">
          Pre-existing materials and methodologies remain my property regardless of the engagement.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">5. Confidentiality</h2>
        <p>
          Both parties agree to keep confidential any sensitive information shared during an engagement and
          not to disclose it to third parties without prior written consent, except where required by law.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-3">
          I may reference the nature of my work (e.g. "organisational development for a technology company")
          in general terms for portfolio purposes, unless a client requests otherwise in writing.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">6. Limitation of liability</h2>
        <p>
          Coaching and consulting services support decision-making and personal or professional development.
          I am not responsible for business outcomes, financial results, or personal decisions made as a
          result of our work together.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-3">
          My liability in connection with any engagement is limited to the total fees paid for that
          specific engagement. I am not liable for indirect, consequential, or special losses.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-3">
          Nothing in these terms limits liability for fraud, death, or personal injury caused by negligence.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">7. Cancellation and rescheduling</h2>
        <p>
          Specific cancellation terms for coaching sessions and project engagements will be set out in the
          relevant agreement. In the absence of a specific agreement:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mt-2 space-y-1">
          <li>Sessions cancelled with more than 48 hours' notice will not be charged.</li>
          <li>Sessions cancelled with less than 48 hours' notice may be charged at the full session rate.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">8. Governing law</h2>
        <p>
          These terms are governed by the laws of <strong>England and Wales</strong>. Any disputes arising
          from these terms or any engagement shall be subject to the exclusive jurisdiction of the courts
          of England and Wales.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">9. Changes to these terms</h2>
        <p>
          I may update these terms from time to time. Any material changes will be communicated to active
          clients before taking effect. Continued use of the website or services after changes constitutes
          acceptance.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">10. Contact</h2>
        <p>
          For any questions about these terms:<br />
          <strong>Fatima Saleh</strong><br />
          <a href="mailto:hello@fatimasaleh.com" class="underline hover:text-burgundy transition-colors">hello@fatimasaleh.com</a>
        </p>
      </section>

    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
